UID:wUyEem4AFDDG_EpBNL5cI
SUMMARY:Lyons Avenue Renaissance Festival
DTSTAMP:20260701T101456Z
DTSTART:20220409T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Lyons Avenue Renaissance Festival celebrates the history\, 
	art\, and culture of Houston’s historic 5th Ward. Activities include Houst
	on’s only egg drop by helicopter! Over 50\,000 goodie-filled\, plastic egg
	s are airdropped at 3 PM on festival day. Featuring live-music stages with
	 authentic blues\,\n\nhttps://thedeluxetheater.com/events/lyons-avenue-ren
	aissance-festival/\n\nFrom The DeLUXE Theater Houston
