	nning film!\nWhatever you think you know about our election systems or Con
	gresswoman Cynthia McKinney\, this film will make you question further why
	 the news media fails to accurately inform the public. Directed by GNN’s I
	an Inaba\, creator\n\nhttps://thedeluxetheater.com/events/american-blackou
